<node id="Speaker 1">
  <data key="d0">Speaker 1</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Speaker 1 explains the differences, structure, and requirements of analytical notes and survey reports.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 1 discusses the limitations of human error in reports compared to AI, emphasizing the need for the bot to handle decision contradictions.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 1 is a participant in the discussion who proposes ideas for document structure and chat-bot functionality.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 1 describes the functional requirements of the chatbot, emphasizing context accumulation and document retrieval capabilities.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 1 is a participant in the discussion who acts as both a functional customer and an IT specialist, explaining project requirements and roles.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 1 is a representative or expert who discusses video recording availability, transcription requirements, and the generation of analytical reports with the team.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 1 expresses satisfaction with the meeting's productivity and bids farewell to the group.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5298ef65e8ebb5fb4ead41ff7e57d97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00f42c5674c08d1c4bf50e1bd4cb1b22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e4b2511c293a18a34a2f9ee769dfe73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f945ba35b34fd5e6c69d4966bc1515c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c017a0092c0a18048d7d3c36d14b3bd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6018f1dfef436c4620437f8b9e42abc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5a47bfb7955d73a940c4b7e3d4379d</data>
  <data key="d4">MeetTest.docx</data>
  <data key="d5">1777022927</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Speaker 2">
  <data key="d0">Speaker 2</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Speaker 2 proposes using a functional template and explains how the system should handle conditional document sections based on project requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 2 discusses interface design preferences, specifically suggesting a single canvas with editing capabilities similar to Canva.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 2 inquires about the scope of context accumulation across projects and clarifies the distinction between model selection and legislative constraints.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 2 is a participant asking questions about scaling, document details, and meeting recordings.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 2 acts as a facilitator, summarizing meeting modes and clarifying mandatory fields for document generation like protocols and analytical notes.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 2 exchanges farewells with Speaker 1 at the conclusion of the meeting.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5298ef65e8ebb5fb4ead41ff7e57d97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00f42c5674c08d1c4bf50e1bd4cb1b22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e4b2511c293a18a34a2f9ee769dfe73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c017a0092c0a18048d7d3c36d14b3bd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6018f1dfef436c4620437f8b9e42abc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5a47bfb7955d73a940c4b7e3d4379d</data>
  <data key="d4">MeetTest.docx</data>
  <data key="d5">1777022928</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Speaker 4">
  <data key="d0">Speaker 4</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Speaker 4 clarifies that a functional template defines the structure of output documents without fixed content, allowing for dynamic generation.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 4 emphasizes the importance of UX and configuring output formats for quick user perception by analysts.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 4 questions the relevance of national legislation (FZ) to the chatbot's underlying language models, suggesting internal tools may have fewer restrictions.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 4 intervenes to suggest taking a pause and allowing others to speak.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 4 proposes concluding the meeting, organizing a video group for transcription practice, and scheduling a follow-up session by the end of the week.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker 4 makes a closing remark about adding punctuation and thanks the group before continuing work in the group.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5298ef65e8ebb5fb4ead41ff7e57d97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00f42c5674c08d1c4bf50e1bd4cb1b22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e4b2511c293a18a34a2f9ee769dfe73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c017a0092c0a18048d7d3c36d14b3bd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6018f1dfef436c4620437f8b9e42abc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5a47bfb7955d73a940c4b7e3d4379d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15fc522d8fcdb2ff85ecb5d791acbe99</data>
  <data key="d4">MeetTest.docx</data>
