  <data key="d0">Meeting Transcript</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Meeting Transcript refers to the text generated from the meeting recording, which Speaker 1 promises to provide as a reference example for the team's testing and practice.&lt;SEP&gt;The Meeting Transcript is a record of a productive meeting where participants discussed protocols, added punctuation, and exchanged farewells.</data>
