<node id="Junior System Analyst">
  <data key="d0">Junior System Analyst</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The Junior System Analyst is a role responsible for preparing meeting protocols, listening to recordings, and documenting details.&lt;SEP&gt;The Junior System Analyst prepares the initial protocol draft but may miss details, misrepresent answers, or fail to recall specific responsibilities agreed upon with the customer.&lt;SEP&gt;The Junior System Analyst reviews the AI-generated draft protocol, resolves inaccuracies, and adds content before passing it to the Senior System Analyst.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-15fc522d8fcdb2ff85ecb5d791acbe99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b81f88fd1f77db0dbb394dd66a377029&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98ed998bba253bb64419418a25b74c96</data>
  <data key="d4">MeetTest.docx</data>
  <data key="d5">1777022930</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Senior System Analyst">
  <data key="d0">Senior System Analyst</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The Senior System Analyst reviews the work of the junior analyst to identify missed details or incorrect information in the protocol.&lt;SEP&gt;The Senior System Analyst reviews the meeting recording to identify details missed by the junior analyst, corrects formulations, and ensures accurate reflection of responsibilities and agreements.&lt;SEP&gt;The Senior System Analyst verifies terminology, performs a full document proofread, corrects issues, and ensures the document meets analytical standards.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-15fc522d8fcdb2ff85ecb5d791acbe99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b81f88fd1f77db0dbb394dd66a377029&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98ed998bba253bb64419418a25b74c96</data>
